{"word":"ἐκφεύγω","slug":"ἐκφεύγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκφεύγω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξοῦμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to flee out</i> or <i>away, escape</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:— <i>to be acquitted</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to escape out of, flee from</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to escape</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li1000'><b>b. </b>of things, <el>ἐκφεύγει μέ τι</el> something <i>escapes</i> me, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}